cu.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid enum value 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing errors and prevent the CU from starting properly.

du.explanation_en: Setting pdsch_AntennaPorts_XP to a negative value -1 will result in invalid antenna port configuration, leading to PDSCH transmission failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 pdsch_AntennaPorts_XP 設定為負值 -1 將導致無效的天線埠配置，造成 PDSCH 傳輸失敗。
